properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 27 at 3:18PM EST until January 28 at 12:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 10 to 20 knots with gusts up to 25 knots
are expected.

* WHERE...The coastal waters from Little Egg Inlet, New Jersey to
Fenwick Island, Delaware.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight until noon on Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating a small
vessel, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO NOON EST TUESDAY
